<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><!--
Splash logo with generous padding to prevent cropping.
Uses 35% padding on all sides to ensure the full logo and "SCANIUM" text
are never cut off on any device size or density.

The Android 12+ SplashScreen API scales icons aggressively, so we need
substantial internal padding within the drawable itself to prevent cropping.
-->
<inset xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:drawable="@drawable/scanium_logo_no_transp"
    android:insetLeft="35%"
    android:insetTop="35%"
    android:insetRight="35%"
    android:insetBottom="35%" />
